1.0.22.name: connect20/Skrill_Hosted_Payment_Solution
1.0.22.description: Skrill’s Hosted Solution accepts payments via cards, over 20 local payment methods and more than 80 banks. Together with Magento, Skrill offer a fully integrated payment solution which can begin accepting payments within hours.
